snippet.title: The Sinking City 2 | World Premiere Trailer (PC, PS5, Xbox Series)
snippet.description:
Explore the flooded city of Arkham in this Lovecraftian survival horror. PC, PS5 & Xbox Series. Coming to Kickstarter soon - subscribe to get notified when it launches https://kck.st/49CIBVR

The Sinking City 2 is a terrifying Lovecraftian journey, powered by Unreal Engine 5. Experience a heart-pounding survival horror as you explore the flooded city of Arkham and fight eldritch monsters beyond human comprehension. Learn more here: https://frogwares.com/the-sinking-city-2-revealed/ 

Get latest news and updates on The Sinking City 2: https://linktr.ee/tsc2_social
